    <p><strong>Prisma</strong>, on the other hand, abstracts away many SQL details, which can make it less flexible in terms of writing custom SQL queries. However, Prisma compensates for this by providing a rich set of features and integrations with other tools and frameworks. It is highly extensible, allowing you to integrate it seamlessly into various parts of your development stack.</p>
