    <p>Ultimately, your choice between Drizzle and Prisma should align with your project's immediate requirements and your long-term vision. Both tools offer valuable solutions for TypeScript-based SQL development, and your decision should be based on your familiarity with SQL, your desired level of customization, and your project's specific performance and compatibility needs.</p>
